"me/jellysquid/mods/lithium/mixin/shapes/precompute_shape_arrays/SimpleVoxelShapeMixin.java"
By: Angeline <jellysquid3@users.noreply.github.com>
As part of: Lithium (https://github.com/CaffeineMC/lithium)
